article.headline: Bolden's 15 points lead UL Monroe over Ecclesia 103-74
article.description: — Jalen Bolden had 15 points in UL Monroe's 103-74 victory against Ecclesia on Monday night.
article.linkText: Bolden's 15 points lead UL Monroe over Ecclesia 103-74
article.story: MONROE, La. -- — Jalen Bolden had 15 points in UL Monroe's 103-74 victory against Ecclesia on Monday night. Bolden finished 6 of 7 from the field for the Warhawks (2-2, Sun Belt Conference). Savion Gallion scored 14 points while going 5 of 8 (2 for 4 from 3-point range), and added five rebounds. Makai Willis had 13 points and was 5 of 8 shooting and 2 of 4 from the free throw line. The Royals were led by Ryan Reed, who recorded 24 points. Ecclesia also got 15 points from Jerry Boston. Brandon Jackson also had 12 points, six rebounds and five assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
